{"tid":889347,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"兩個月走遍中南美（一）－墨西哥亡靈節","createTime":"2018-11-04T13:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T20:36:55.000Z","uid":72476,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"871e7624714678851b2c03cd8f819e57ef6810e2","tid":889347,"uid":72476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:40:51.000Z","msg":"話說小弟心血來潮，決定同老婆一齊辭左依家份工，放幾個月假去下中南美洲旅行，計劃用兩個月遊走四個國家：墨西哥﹑秘魯﹑阿根廷同烏拉圭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mtBGQVL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmtBGQVL.jpg&h=1e537a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n計劃由北玩向南，第一站撞正墨西哥一年一度既亡靈節。<br />\n亡靈節係墨西哥一個普天同慶既歡樂節日。墨西哥人抱住歡迎親人返黎人間團聚既心去大肆慶祝，大家睇過pixar既玩轉極樂園（Coco）應該略知一二。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t52F6u7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft52F6u7.jpg&h=2a15830c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而係墨西哥既第一個落腳點，係全國第二大城瓜達拉哈拉。（Guadalajara）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps想睇更多相同片既可以follow小弟既facebook page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/梁凌均-279839865976035/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%87%8C%E5%9D%87-279839865976035%2F&d=Wr2k4cSpxOUQjfIJ1fi7q%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=0ebb410e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/梁凌均-279839865976035/</a>"},{"pid":"55dd4583545fa4c847a09295d755aa0ac9a592f0","tid":889347,"uid":159768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"871e7624714678851b2c03cd8f819e57ef6810e2","tid":889347,"uid":72476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:40:51.000Z","msg":"話說小弟心血來潮，決定同老婆一齊辭左依家份工，放幾個月假去下中南美洲旅行，計劃用兩個月遊走四個國家：墨西哥﹑秘魯﹑阿根廷同烏拉圭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mtBGQVL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmtBGQVL.jpg&h=1e537a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n計劃由北玩向南，第一站撞正墨西哥一年一度既亡靈節。<br />\n亡靈節係墨西哥一個普天同慶既歡樂節日。墨西哥人抱住歡迎親人返黎人間團聚既心去大肆慶祝，大家睇過pixar既玩轉極樂園（Coco）應該略知一二。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t52F6u7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft52F6u7.jpg&h=2a15830c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而係墨西哥既第一個落腳點，係全國第二大城瓜達拉哈拉。（Guadalajara）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps想睇更多相同片既可以follow小弟既facebook page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/梁凌均-279839865976035/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%87%8C%E5%9D%87-279839865976035%2F&d=Wr2k4cSpxOUQjfIJ1fi7q%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=0ebb410e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/梁凌均-279839865976035/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:42:05.000Z","msg":"衷心一頂，足球到以家，都會支持你"},{"pid":"6fdd944fb436d150c8e6fc3ffebf613d16d03ab6","tid":889347,"uid":72476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T14:01:58.000Z","msg":"Day 1<br />\n之前不斷聽人講話墨西哥係一個治安差既地方，加上當日落機已經凌晨十二點幾，喺機場已經唔敢掉以輕心。見到好多人排隊買authorized taxi既飛個心都定d，起碼知道唔係個d會車左你去唔知邊度既「黑的」。一張的士飛由機場去市中心，盛惠300 pesos（140蚊港紙）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2SVkuvx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2SVkuvx.jpg&h=e799ff48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FwSnHQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFwSnHQE.jpg&h=eb3c9969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大概45分鐘車程，市區周邊既建築物入黑之後好有大陸感覺，快快手返酒店沖個涼就訓左覺。<br />\n<br />\n第二日起身一落街，個感覺完全唔同<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dvtqFFP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdvtqFFP.jpg&h=a934dea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8fsbBev.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8fsbBev.jpg&h=decf1c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥人好鍾意塗鴉，一街既牆都係五顏六色既graffiti，而由於天主教係墨西哥既國教，好多塗鴉都係十字架﹑聖母同耶穌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cvxKWer.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcvxKWer.jpg&h=cb751be5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隔一兩條街就會見到d好標緻既噴泉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qYpYgeE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqYpYgeE.jpg&h=cfcaae4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬車亦係瓜達拉哈拉隨處可見，200 pesos坐半粒鐘，唔算好貴（西班牙個d要成30歐羅）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CS23smp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCS23smp.jpg&h=89be7133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎到墨西哥當然要試下當地美食，呢間野叫fish taco，距離市中心十分鐘腳程，係一間幾出名既當地人至愛，排隊都排左十幾分鐘，叫左一塊taco一件burrito，都係70蚊pesos到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VwaHHUK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVwaHHUK.jpg&h=53d30b34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食食下有幾個樂師走過黎拉小提琴，墨西哥人食野都要音樂襯托<br />\n（貼士俾幾多隨意）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L8OqFH6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL8OqFH6.jpg&h=ab9fc5f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oum4bPV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOum4bPV.jpg&h=ff0f024a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n墨西哥旗到處飄揚"},{"pid":"62ddcc1e2347f3c610c3f440628bd5c4d28c74aa","tid":889347,"uid":138677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T14:08:41.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421d62b37f97ff6a9ce992cea0bf0ece548b5d56","tid":889347,"uid":117585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T14:19:38.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"6101cff1e2500ebe8666d7c7be64a33e454347cf","tid":889347,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T14:20:26.000Z","msg":"打屎忽先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f737ae0d34defab49274eb05cdf45c41c24a4b","tid":889347,"uid":147628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"871e7624714678851b2c03cd8f819e57ef6810e2","tid":889347,"uid":72476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:40:51.000Z","msg":"話說小弟心血來潮，決定同老婆一齊辭左依家份工，放幾個月假去下中南美洲旅行，計劃用兩個月遊走四個國家：墨西哥﹑秘魯﹑阿根廷同烏拉圭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mtBGQVL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmtBGQVL.jpg&h=1e537a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n計劃由北玩向南，第一站撞正墨西哥一年一度既亡靈節。<br />\n亡靈節係墨西哥一個普天同慶既歡樂節日。墨西哥人抱住歡迎親人返黎人間團聚既心去大肆慶祝，大家睇過pixar既玩轉極樂園（Coco）應該略知一二。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t52F6u7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft52F6u7.jpg&h=2a15830c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而係墨西哥既第一個落腳點，係全國第二大城瓜達拉哈拉。（Guadalajara）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps想睇更多相同片既可以follow小弟既facebook page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/梁凌均-279839865976035/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%87%8C%E5%9D%87-279839865976035%2F&d=Wr2k4cSpxOUQjfIJ1fi7q%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=0ebb410e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/梁凌均-279839865976035/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"lm 極想去南美!!!!!"},{"pid":"73aa7dc43b026d19d2018ecb6442e10f1c32e1f6","tid":889347,"uid":64155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T14:37:40.000Z","msg":"Coco!!!<br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fcbc05ac4f168e2428f902d15b2fcfdc76388d4","tid":889347,"uid":72476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T14:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6kBLFT1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kBLFT1.jpg&h=1ae7481e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TsQ1d8q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTsQ1d8q.jpg&h=0f023565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XFqkuGX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXFqkuGX.jpg&h=bcce3b83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eia4Wm2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEia4Wm2.jpg&h=038a4ac9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎到一個叫PALACIO DE GOBIERNO（英譯Government Palace） 既地方，講述瓜達拉哈拉既歷史<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2AAiAL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2AAiAL.jpg&h=6652d797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會議廳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDXnH2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDXnH2a.jpg&h=0b96737d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJos&eacute; Clemente Orozco係墨西哥一位享負盛名既藝術家，作品講述人生苦難，係其中一個影響墨西哥藝術文化最深遠既人物：主樓梯呢幅畫叫做The People and Its Leaders，所講既故事係墨西哥人走向獨立既辛酸史。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bPMLFT0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbPMLFT0.jpg&h=7acec1fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QR6S5fD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQR6S5fD.jpg&h=9050498d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oc17T9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOc17T9d.jpg&h=19bb9b41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HgWosvg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHgWosvg.png&h=e665751c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瓜達拉哈拉廣場係城市既中心點，呢度有大型音樂會既場地﹑劇院同埋大型熟食市場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mzoViFH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmzoViFH.jpg&h=5efd3979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w15Xw0J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw15Xw0J.jpg&h=ccfd6494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n價錢超值既雪糕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHWS5kE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHWS5kE.jpg&h=720b1cde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8LOaRV1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8LOaRV1.jpg&h=cc659a19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周圍都係天主教教堂，全部開放參觀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U9zpWum.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU9zpWum.jpg&h=ecb76348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hfwvR2H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhfwvR2H.jpg&h=4537b7f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旅客區附近仲有好多唔同既食店。<br />\n墨西哥最出名既食物原材料有<span style=\"color: red;\">粟米﹑芝士同醬料</span>，基本上第一日到埗早午晚三餐已經試晒，因為成條街除左本地墨西哥野食之外就再無其他<br />\n（有幾間中國人開既餐廳，不過係一睇就知好撚難食個d）<br />\n（成個世界都係中國人）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L0rS5kK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0rS5kK.jpg&h=34bd13db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夜晚廣場個景真係好靚"},{"pid":"8b60f26b94058236b58df609a8d4c49dc575d1ea","tid":889347,"uid":72476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T14:50:32.000Z","msg":"<strong>Day 2</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8h9dPQv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8h9dPQv.jpg&h=464e452c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說之前一直以為剪紙藝術同埋喺coco入面出現過既萬壽菊﹑祭壇都係亡靈節既gimmick，經墨西哥朋友解說先知道原來亡靈節（dia de muertos）﹑神獸（alebrijes）同剪紙藝術（papel picado）係三種獨立既墨西哥文化，係coco製作人走遍墨西哥將三種唔同既文化融合電影裡面，令好多人以為呢d都係亡靈節既附屬品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VE269Ra.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVE269Ra.jpg&h=c61b5fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6yA4Wwi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yA4Wwi.jpg&h=0810860a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPapel picado係一種深入民間既墨西哥藝術，一年365日都可以喺墨西哥各大城市既街頭見到，瓜達拉哈拉當然都唔例外，望住呢d剪紙感受亡靈節特別有氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g5uELpS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg5uELpS.jpg&h=12825c9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SrLTPRD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSrLTPRD.jpg&h=6115e429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n離開左downtown，去返一個比較發達既地區，有酒吧有商場有銀行，同尋日行既野完全唔一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sS7GeiP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsS7GeiP.jpg&h=7a1aa113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入左一間酒吧試左兩種唔同味道同顏色既啤酒，都係瓜達拉哈拉特產。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gRZtDLJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgRZtDLJ.jpg&h=5a6509fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QXoezi4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXoezi4.jpg&h=d75acc05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n離開左酒吧已經五點幾，大街中間擺左好多擋攤，原來呢區每日黃昏都會有個大型跳蚤市場賣精品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1tViMa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1tViMa.jpg&h=86af750d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QqSODLL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQqSODLL.jpg&h=5748de8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QRJKb5M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQRJKb5M.jpg&h=aa7d5bdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n臨近亡靈節，當然唔少得唔同顏色既骷髏頭同埋萬壽菊製品，買左個白色骷髏頭，價值100 pesos。"},{"pid":"e38c7b671e2597cbcc9dae25b0b77967be8094b0","tid":889347,"uid":3039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T14:51:24.000Z","msg":"COCO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c9baa31e121c2228d2bf5c614e8732463681b6","tid":889347,"uid":72476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T15:02:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>Day 3</strong><br />\n今日有墨西哥朋友做導遊，去左一間幾高檔既地道餐廳食早餐，價錢都唔算好貴，三份野加埋400 pesos到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qHY2Jfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqHY2Jfb.jpg&h=20abfeec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TfeQR8y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfeQR8y.jpg&h=57d95225&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n埋單後侍應送左兩舊咁既野俾我地，原來係糖。墨西哥人除左食taco仲好嗜甜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/asc3sG3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fasc3sG3.jpg&h=01d95de3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有睇過小弟既故都知我好鍾意足球。朋友特登車左我地去呢個好似太空船一樣既球場，係墨西哥球隊Guadalajara Chivas既主場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/todeznb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftodeznb.jpg&h=622d0241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQcGenN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQcGenN.jpg&h=acc85596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKyNUnj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKyNUnj.jpg&h=482c12e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xwqc5t3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwqc5t3.jpg&h=d865a936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nChivas喺墨西哥既地位就等同英國既曼聯利物浦，長年都係國內最受歡迎球隊，仲曾經入過南美自由盃決賽。近年雖然戰績差，但球迷數量依然冠絕整個墨西哥。<br />\n<br />\n夜晚，墨西哥朋友帶我地去睇墨西哥dance show <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GR7bBBa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGR7bBBa.jpg&h=067fc798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mecu7HS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmecu7HS.jpg&h=9930aed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聞說話呢隻鷹跌左落黎成個劇院會倒塌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/riRPogb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FriRPogb.jpg&h=f5071e67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n計下數，今日連埋睇show兩個人只係用左1500 pesos到，墨西哥既洗費真係好抵（個時未去cancun唔知原來城市之間物價可以差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"b7e9300ed6e7ab80ce599a32594ea21130e06888","tid":889347,"uid":72476,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T15:17:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>Day 4</strong><br />\n瓜達拉哈拉既最後一日黎到Tlaquepague，一個好傳統既旅遊小鎮，由市中心搭uber大概四十分鐘到，一落車就見到條條街都係剪紙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yJPmeqV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyJPmeqV.jpg&h=72316c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AEyNUqX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAEyNUqX.jpg&h=2a517b82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎到呢度，最想睇就係涼亭，coco一開始主角幫人擦鞋同埋借結他既地方原型就係呢d亭<br />\n<br />\n夜景<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72AAiUj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72AAiUj.jpg&h=149ca888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個廣場都係白鴿，目測有成幾百隻，有個肥女人一路餵一路捉住d白鴿黎錫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 墨西哥真係咩人都有<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8gKmerR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8gKmerR.jpg&h=9a982a41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有見及此，我地都去七仔買左件紙包蛋糕餵鴿，d白鴿多到餵晒成件蛋糕都未夠<br />\n<br />\n呢個小鎮好多多精品店同跳蚤市場，基本上都係賺旅客錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6orvSdo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6orvSdo.jpg&h=aba86c9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OnWf3ko.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOnWf3ko.jpg&h=123d5a9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCoco入面既曲神像<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1G3NUr0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1G3NUr0.jpg&h=40b5a5d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n擦鞋業<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k0zA3kp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk0zA3kp.jpg&h=b93bf55b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瓜達拉哈拉其中一樣舉世知名既特產係龍舌蘭酒，試左一杯38度酒精溝果汁既fruta tequila，冇想像中咁「哽」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sKTRBFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsKTRBFh.jpg&h=b2921fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢度周圍都有管弦樂隊表演<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VbCSk60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVbCSk60.jpg&h=b3989061&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一街都係papel picado<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gfs690G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgfs690G.jpg&h=183ce43d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n離開瓜達拉哈拉既下一站係坎昆（cancun），一個加勒比海度假聖地。<br />\n<br />\n有人想知再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8db6ac180095ee86179ddf430662f6d0d7b04fb","tid":889347,"uid":1841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T15:35:53.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb76d0ee414b742496a258c07a096fc581aa5200","tid":889347,"uid":72476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55dd4583545fa4c847a09295d755aa0ac9a592f0","tid":889347,"uid":159768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"871e7624714678851b2c03cd8f819e57ef6810e2","tid":889347,"uid":72476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:40:51.000Z","msg":"話說小弟心血來潮，決定同老婆一齊辭左依家份工，放幾個月假去下中南美洲旅行，計劃用兩個月遊走四個國家：墨西哥﹑秘魯﹑阿根廷同烏拉圭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mtBGQVL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmtBGQVL.jpg&h=1e537a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n計劃由北玩向南，第一站撞正墨西哥一年一度既亡靈節。<br />\n亡靈節係墨西哥一個普天同慶既歡樂節日。墨西哥人抱住歡迎親人返黎人間團聚既心去大肆慶祝，大家睇過pixar既玩轉極樂園（Coco）應該略知一二。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t52F6u7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft52F6u7.jpg&h=2a15830c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而係墨西哥既第一個落腳點，係全國第二大城瓜達拉哈拉。（Guadalajara）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps想睇更多相同片既可以follow小弟既facebook page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/梁凌均-279839865976035/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%87%8C%E5%9D%87-279839865976035%2F&d=Wr2k4cSpxOUQj